title: Newly Updated! Easy Access to Tollway, 35 and 635! Covered Parking
posting_body: ['A fusion of suburban comfort with vibrant urban vibes, the garden-style community offers renovated homes and premium amenities in Far North Dallas.', 'Located off Dallas North Tollway and George Bush Turnpike, Parkway.', ' Conveniently located near Willow Bend Mall, residents are minutes away from shops, restaurants and nightlife.', 'Each apartment features an open floor plan with renovated interiors and high-quality finishes.', 'Living rooms and dining areas include nine-foot ceilings lined with crown molding and beautiful wood-style flooring.', 'Upgraded kitchens gleam with new appliances, granite countertops, wood flooring and custom cabinetry.', 'Achieve ultimate relaxation with fantastic amenities throughout the community.', 'Two sparkling pools and a gourmet kitchen create an outdoor resort.', 'With carport parking, hot tub, pool, a 24/7 fitness and cardio center and optional garage and storage units.', 'Conveniently located near Willow Bend Mall, residents are minutes away from shops, restaurants and nightlife.', 'Call Desiree@ DASH', 'show contact info', 'Mention ad D320']
